Output docs/demo-overlays.gif
Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 80ms

Hide
Type "cd /tmp/grove-demo/rails-app"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show
Type "./bin/grove"
Enter
Sleep 1s
Down
Sleep 300ms
Type "d"
Sleep 1s
Type "n"
Sleep 800ms
Escape
Sleep 500ms
Type "?"
Sleep 1s
Type "?"
Sleep 500ms
Type "a"
Sleep 1s
Escape
Sleep 500ms
Type "q"
